in
executing
it!
he
could
ride
to
London
at
any
time.
It
was
impossible
to
say
how
much
he
should
be
gratified
by
being
employed
on
such
an
errand."
"He
was
too
good!
she
could
not
endure
the
thought!
she
would
not
give
him
such
