minutes
settled
the
business.
Mr.
Elton
was
to
take
the
drawing
to
London,
chuse
the
frame,
and
give
the
directions;
and
Emma
thought
she
could
so
pack
it
as
to
ensure
its
safety
without
much
incommoding
him,
while
he
seemed
mostly
